high_descs: Little bit move towards left and walk straight to reach the sofa
Take a knife from the sofa
Turn right and take few steps and turn left to reach the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the knife in it and close the oven
Turn back and once again turn back to reach the shelf on which oven is placed
Put the knife on the shelf which is below the oven
Head towards the oven
Open the oven and take a potato piece from the oven and close it
Turn back and walk straight and turn left and walk straight to reach the fridge
Open the fridge and put the potato piece into the fridge and close it. After few seconds, open the door and take the potato piece out and again close the fridge.
Turn back and walk straight. Then turn right to reach the side table
Put the potato piece on the side table
